Share this on WhatsAppSpread the lovePopular veteran Juju Artiste, Soko music crooner, Wonder Dayo Kujore is dead, a reliable source from the family has revealed.
Cause of his death is yet to be disclosed as at the time of putting this report together.
National Daily reliably gathered the singer was confirmed dead at the Lagos State University Teaching Hospital (LASUTH) Ikeja, Lagos.
READ ALSO: Soldier shoots man dead for not yielding seat in beer parlour
Wonder Dayo Kujore was born on the 4th of April 1958 at Robiyan, Ogun, Nigeria.
His fans ‘baptised’ him with the name “Wonder”  after being impressed with his dexterity in playing the guitar and keyboard at a tender age, while he was alive in one of his interviews, Kujore said, ”I was very young then when I started playing the guitar and keyboard.
